Location is in Clementi.

MOE School environment
Monday - Friday only
9.00am - 6.30pm (incl. 1 hr lunch break)

Job Role &amp; Responsibilities
Provide logistical support for school events and functions including arranging of furniture and equipment
Provide support in general upkeep of school equipment and workplace
Perform gate duties&nbsp;
Perform traffic control to ensure safety of students moving in and out of premises

Requirements
Minimum must have completed PSLE
Preferably with some experience in general upkeep/cleaning of equipment/ workplace and simple logistical duties
Able to converse in English. Able to converse in Mandarin will be advantageous
Fit and able to move furniture and equipment
Able to take instructions from supervisor

